How Does VOIPo Work?
1) When you order our service, you can select a new phone number from over 7,000 available areas or transfer your existing number.
2) We'll ship you a VOIPo Phone Adapter. When you receive it, simply plug it into your broadband internet connection and plug your normal telephones into it. 
3) All done! Use your phone just like you normally would. When you place calls, the adapter sends the calls out through your internet connection to the VOIPo network instead of the regular phone network.


 


